-- MOVES-Macquarie Capital names Thynne managing director of FIG in Asia  
-- 
-- Thu Sep 04, 2014 03:59AM EDT
-- None



Sept 4 (Reuters) - Global investment banking firm Macquarie Capital appointed Grenville Thynne managing director and head of Financial Institutions Group in Asia.

Thynne joins Macquarie from ING Group <ING.AS> where he was managing director and head of corporate finance in Asia.